# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NATLY - ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES TEMPLATE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# DO NOT commit .env.local to Git!

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC VARIABLES (Frontend - Safe to expose in browser)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These variables are prefixed with VITE_ and bundled into the client build
# They are visible to anyone inspecting the browser

VITE_API_URL=https://your-site.netlify.app
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here
VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_recaptcha_site_key_here

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PRIVATE VARIABLES (Backend Only - NEVER expose these!)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set these in Netlify Dashboard → Site Settings → Environment Variables
# DO NOT put real values in this file!

# JWT_SECRET=your_random_32_char_secret_here
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key_here
# RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEVELOPMENT SETUP
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in your actual values in .env.local
# 3. Never commit .env.local (it's in .gitignore)
# 4. For production, set secrets in Netlify Environment Variables